<item>
 <title>World transformation movement</title>
 <link>https://www.portlandhumanists.org/content/world-transformation-movement</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-taxonomy-forums field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Forums:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; rel=&quot;sioc:has_container&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/forums/general-discussion&quot; typeof=&quot;sioc:Container sioc:Forum&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;General Discussion&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/category/tags/world-transformation-movement&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;World transformation movement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hey guys I&#039;m trying to seek feedback from our general membership, about this world transformation movement. I think Dr Griffith, has really nailed it down with his theory on The human condition. But I would love some lively discussion with this group. As I think it&#039;s right down our alley is humanist. Please go on the web and seek this out and at least see his presentation, if not download his free book and study up on a little. I&#039;ve come to my own conclusions which differ greatly from Dr Griffith. But I would really like some feedback from like mines. So do check it out and please post here I&#039;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
